description:
Danny recaps this week's Southern Charm, which features the cast skiing in Colorado. They hit the slopes for some antics, and then have a weed-infused dinner that leaves some of them very high, all the while Kathryn watches WWHL clips on her phone. Meanwhile back in Charleston, Naomi's punishment for not going on the cast trip is meeting with Ashley.
